> 
> //Both run off down the corridor, Farnsworth lagging somewhat. McIver is left standing in the doorway, alone.//
> 
> 
> //She turns, and begins walking to her bed, slightly unsteadily. She sits down and stares out of the door at nothing in particular. Her face is blank.//
> 
> 
> **McIver:** Huh.
> 
